sentence: Precursors of T cells originate in the bone marrow from which they migrate via bloodstream into thymic cortex, where they encounter stromal cell s including cTECs, which form the microenvironment crucial for proliferation and development of T cells by expression of DLL4 (delta-like notch ligand 4), cytokine s IL-7, TGFÎ² or stem cell factor and chemokine s CCL25, CXCL12 or CCRL1 etc.
